---
title: Grill Mates Pork Meatloaves with Brown Sugar Bourbon Seasoning, Mashed Potatoes & Green Beans
description: Finding yourself in a meatloaf rut? Enter: this sweet and savory version. First, we blend ground pork with a not-so-secret ingredient—grated apple—for subtle sweetness and added moisture. Next, we form the mixture into mini loaves so everyone gets their own. The pièce de résistance? We infuse the usual ketchup glaze with a brown sugar bourbon seasoning for smoky, caramelized notes. Add sides of mashed potatoes and roasted green beans, and your routine meat-and-potatoes dinner doesn’t stand a chance.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/brown-sugar-bourbon-pork-meatloaves-ae2e251d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/grill-mates-pork-meatloaves-5f7dcf7a8220af61bc7d7531-0fc13d3a.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/grill-mates-pork-meatloaves-5f7dcf7a8220af61bc7d7531
time required: 50 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 710 kcal
  fat: 39 g
  saturated fat: 16 g
